UC03 ..> SYS1 : <<include>>
UC04 ..> SYS2 : <<include>>
UC04 ..> SYS3 : <<include>>
UC04 ..> SYS4 : <<include>>
S5   ..> SYS5 : <<include>>
S6   ..> SYS5 : <<include>>

